---
// Get Started section component for landing page
---

<section class="max-w-4xl w-full mt-16 mb-16">
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Get Started</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Initialize Rafters in your project:</p>
        <code class="block bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm">
          npx rafters init
        </code>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Add your first component:</p>
        <code class="block bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm">
          npx rafters add button
        </code>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          That's it. You now have a mathematically-sound, AI-readable design system.
          Components work immediately with grayscale defaults. Run Studio later to add your
          brand personality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>